{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- PLEASE ADD CATEGORIES AND INTERWIKIS AT THE BOTTOM OF THIS PAGE -->

== Usage ==
{{Template notes
|The editor placing this template in an article should promptly begin a discussion on the article's talk page.  In the absence of any discussion, or if the discussion has become dormant, then this tag may be removed by any editor. 
|The purpose of this group of templates is to attract editors with different viewpoints to edit articles that need additional insight.  This template should not be used as a [[badge of shame]]. 
|This template should only be applied to articles that are reasonably believed to misrepresent the views of [[WP:RS|high-quality reliable sources]] in the subject.  The personal beliefs of Wikipedia's editors are irrelevant. 
|Do not add this to a page more than a reasonable number of times, instead use one of the other templates mentioned [[#Templates|below]] instead.
}}

Add <code><nowiki>{{POV statement}}</nowiki></code> after a statement or [[posit]] to signify that just that statement may not be entirely without bias.

=== Parameters ===
* {{para|1}} (or an empty parameter): specifies the section on the talk page the "disputed" link points to.
* {{para|date}}: the date that the tag was placed.

Thus:

:{{Tlx|POV statement|Objection|date{{=}}{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}

produces

:{{POV statement|Objection|date=January 2013}}, where "disputed" links to Talk:Article_name#Objection. Hovering over the link "neutrality" reveals the date that the tag was placed.

==Redirects==
{{list redirects|Template:POV statement}}

== TemplateData ==
{{TemplateData header}}
<templatedata>
{
    "description": "Use this inline template to tag a statement that may not be entirely without bias. The editor placing the template must start a relevant talk page discussion.",
	"format": "inline",
	"params": {
		"date": {
			"label": "Month and year",
			"description": "Month and year of tagging; e.g., 'January 2013', but not 'jan13'",
			"type": "string",
			"autovalue": "May 2025",
			"example": "January 2013",
			"suggested": true
		},
		"1": {
			"label": "Section name on talk page",
			"description": "Section name on talk page where further information or discussion can be found",
			"type": "string"
		}
	},
	"paramOrder": [
		"date",
		"1"
	]
}
</templatedata>

